Package assignmenttests.classlevel.products.attribute

Class AttributeSignatureTest

java.lang.Object
assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
assignmenttests.classlevel.products.attribute.AttributeSignatureTest
All Implemented Interfaces:
assignmenttests.AssignmentTest, assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTest
@TestInstance(PER_CLASS) public class AttributeSignatureTest extends assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
Test class for verifying the attributes of a class. This class extends ClassTestBase and performs various tests on class attributes such as existence, data type, default value, and modifiers (static and final).
